g \in L^1 ([0,\infty))
\displaystyle\int_0^\infty g(x)dx =1
f:[0,\infty)\rightarrow \mathbb{R}
n \displaystyle\int_0^1 f(x+t) g(nt) dt \rightarrow f(x)
n\rightarrow \infty
x\in \mathbb{R}
