y=nt
\chi_{[0,n)}
\tag{1}n \displaystyle\int_0^1 f(x+t) g(nt) dt=\int_0^nf(x+\frac{y}{n})g(y)dy=\int_0^\infty \chi_{[0,n)}(y)f(x+\frac{y}{n})g(y)dy.
